				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Upon interacting with the tentacle living inside the tower's wall, player is faced with several options to choose from. \r\n- Take a sample (can be used in Mig mini quest)\r\n- Poke to see how it reacts\r\n- Examine it to learn more about it\r\n- Tear it down with brute force\r\nDamage being done onto the tentacle will trigger a reaction from the Absolute"
